OL,3,GNorth East
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FA fine and frosty start in many
OL,6,Fplaces, with areas of mist and fog
OL,7,Fclearing to a dry day. Then dry
OL,8,Flargely sunny for northern areas but
OL,9,Fcloudier further south. Slight milder
OL,10,Ffor most places compared to Friday.
OL,11,
OL,12,CTonight:FDry start with clear spells,
OL,13,Fmainly for northern areas. Cloud soon
OL,14,Fspreads north this evening, bringing
OL,15,Fpatchy light rain and hill fog
OL,16,Fovernight.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
