OL,3,GNorth East
OL,4,
OL,5,CSunday:FOutbreaks of rain through the
OL,6,Fmorning, perhaps with some occasional
OL,7,Fheavier bursts. Becoming largely dry
OL,8,Fthrough the afternoon but remaining
OL,9,Fpredominantly cloudy. Early hill fog
OL,10,Fgradually lifts.
OL,11,
OL,12,COutlook for Monday to Wednesday:FMonday
OL,13,Fand Tuesday often cloudy but mainly
OL,14,Fdry, with best chance of bright spells
OL,15,FTuesday afternoon. Wednesday windy
OL,16,Fwith sunshine and scattered showers.
OL,17,FTemperatures generally near or
OL,18,Fslightly above average.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
